name: China Princess: Kang Cing Wi
description:
Image size: 29.7 x 42 cm, CMYK, 300 dpi

Jero Luh is all called as Barong Landung Luh as image of China princess who called Kang Cing Wi married by Jaya pangus king in Dalem Balikang story.

This story comes from traditional Balinese society. This work is about the cultural exchange between China and Bali - Indonesia
